column2: "Gah... I really wish I could talk to Aina a bit more often..."
"Under Garoa's watchful eye, nobody really has the guts to approach her..."
"Garoa is strictly overprotective of Aina, but I realize that's probably just how he dotes on his little girl."
"He's just so worried about her all the time, so he never lets her out of his sight."
